---
title: Creamy Pork & Bacon Spaghetti with Extra Parmesan & Balsamic Salad
description: This pasta night is going to be our most delicious yet, with diced bacon and pork mince providing extra savoury flavour! Golden ropes of slurpable spaghetti are tangled up in a creamy, meaty sauce for this match made in heaven. Add some freshness with a crisp salad, and dig in.
